# Strengths

- Produces the correct total.
- Easy to understand.
- Simple control flow.
- Minimal complexity.

---

# Weaknesses

- Duplicate iteration over the same data.
- Hardcoded item categories.
- Limited scalability.
- Missing documentation and type hints.

---

# Recommendations

- Iterate through the shopping cart only once.
- Eliminate duplicated calculations.
- Improve extensibility by reducing dependence on hardcoded values.
- Add documentation and type annotations.
- Write unit tests to verify behavior after refactoring.

